=Details on the WikiSprint Procedures=

==General Background Information:==

The P2P Foundation's wiki has section page on Brazil, with introductory material that may be considered a bit outdated, but will be renewed and updated thanks to the WikiSprint. You can access to it from [[:Category:Brazil|this link]].

To find general information on p2p and participatory developments in Brazil, see our bookmark collections at [http://del.icio.us/mbauwens/P2P-Brazil Delicious] and [http://www.diigo.com/user/mbauwens/P2P-Brazil Diigo]

[http://meipi.org/mappingthecommons.list.php?category=4  An example] of a similar mapping effort in Athens, Greece.

